mg":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11575,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/greeting-visit-qabr-madinah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14653,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ziyarah: Greeting the Prophet at his grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you greets me with peace (at his grave) except Allah returns my spirit, that I may return his greeting of peace.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2041 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17347,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/worst-people-graves-masajid\/","url_meta":{"origin":14653,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Worst people turn graves into places of worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the worst of people are those upon whom the Hour is established while they are alive, and those who take graves as places of worship.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4132 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32411,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/two-men-punished-in-graves\/","url_meta":{"origin":14653,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Two men punished for backbiting, uncleanliness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by two graves and he said, \u201cVerily, they are both being punished, but not for a sin difficult to avoid. As for one, he is punished for the habit of soiling himself with urine. As for the other,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17418,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/believer-shaded-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14653,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Believers will be shaded by their charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, charity will extinguish the heat of the graves for their people. Only the believer can seek shade on the Day of Resurrection in the shade of his charity.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 3076 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14653",